<example>
  <title>Print a triangle</title>
  <program>
size = int(input("Enter size of mystical triangle: "))
           
y = 0
while y < size:
    x = 0
    while x < size:
        if x <= y:
            print("*", end='')   # print an asterisk without newline
        else:
            print(" ", end='')   # print a space without newline
        x += 1
    print()    # print a newline
    y += 1

  </program>
  <description>A triangle of side and height from the input size is printed. Actually prints a square with some locations printing an (empty) space and other locations stars.  The stars' locations form a triangle.</description>
